# Earth-Harmony-Framework

**Exact-value resonance engineering for the next era of technology.**

This repository contains the complete Earth-Harmony-Framework — a unified, integer-based operating system that eliminates torsional debt and restores perfect resonance across terrestrial systems. The framework is built on the 360-day harmonic baseline, zero-debt operation, the 5/3 Hz aqueous refractive bridge, 3-6-9 weighting, and acoustic levitation as experimental validation.

### Core Axiom
Physical reality operates on exact integer cycles. Rounding and floating-point approximations are the last remaining source of systemic inefficiency. When models are forced to the exact 360-day grid, torsional debt collapses to zero, unlocking zero-resistance energy transfer and emergent-gravity suppression.

